{"type":"text","timestamp":1782380218264,"sessionID":"ses_101de3b79ffel3ckx0Q2nI7Wic","part":{"id":"prt_efe23ac65001S9b3iOilbYpxcp","messageID":"msg_efe236bf7001m9j0EXWdzdUI9Q","sessionID":"ses_101de3b79ffel3ckx0Q2nI7Wic","type":"text","text":"I’ve confirmed the source rows include several static-analysis false positives for permissions/notifications in these screens. I’m going to record those as source-evidence non-applicable/deferred equivalents in the matrix rather than fabricate platform behavior, while strengthening the real onboarding/login/profile rows with concrete target endpoints.","time":{"start":1782380211301,"end":1782380218263}}}
